HEADWORD: Tonicity
<hw>To*nic"i*ty</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Physiol.)</fld>
<def>The state of healthy tension or partial contraction of muscle
fibers while at rest; tone; tonus.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Tonight</ent>⟦br⟧
